cript Purpose:
   This script performs quality checks to validate the integrity
   and accuracy of the Gold Layer. These checks ensure:
   - Uniqueness of surrogate keys in dimension tables.
   - Referential integrity between fact and dimension tables.
   - Validation of relationships in the data model for analytica
sage Notes:
   - Investigate and resolve any discrepancies found during the 
================================================================
/
- ==============================================================
- Checking 'gold.dim_customers'
- ==============================================================
- Check for Uniqueness of Customer Key in gold.dim_customers
- Expectation: No results 
ELECT 
   customer_key,
   COUNT(*) AS duplicate_count
ROM gold.dim_customers
ROUP BY customer_key
AVING COUNT(*) > 1;
- ==============================================================
- Checking 'gold.product_key'
- ==============================================================
- Check for Uniqueness of Product Key in gold.dim_products
- Expectation: No results 
ELECT 
   product_key,
   COUNT(*) AS duplicate_count
ROM gold.dim_products
ROUP BY product_key
AVING COUNT(*) > 1;
- ==============================================================
- Checking 'gold.fact_sales'
- ==============================================================
- Check the data model connectivity between fact and dimensions
ELECT * 
ROM gold.fact_sales f
EFT JOIN gold.dim_customers c
N c.customer_key = f.customer_key
EFT JOIN gold.dim_products p
N p.product_key = f.product_key
HERE p.product_key IS NULL OR c.customer_key IS NULL  
